edu.usc.scrc.PriorityPruner
Class Result

java.lang.Object
  edu.usc.scrc.PriorityPruner.Result
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Object>
public class Result
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Object>

This class represents a result record between a pair of SNPs. The data from this object is displayed in the LD output file. The class implements Comparable interface so that objects of this type can be sorted by the position of the second SNP (ParterPos).
